---
import { Image } from "astro:assets";
import Layout from "@/layouts/Project.astro";
import Heading from "@/components/ui/Heading.astro";
import Text from "@/components/ui/Text.astro";
import ProjectContnetWrapper from "@/components/ui/ProjectContnetWrapper.astro";
import SwiperSlider from "@/components/ui/SwiperSlider.astro";
import { loadImages } from "@/utils/loadImages";

import detail1Img from "@/assets/alfaDecor/1.png";
import detail2Img from "@/assets/alfaDecor/2.png";
import logoImg from "@/assets/logo/alfalogo-min.png";

const title = "Alfa Bank - Alfa Travel";
const years = "2023-2025";

const imageModulesFirst = import.meta.glob<{ default: ImageMetadata }>(
  "/src/assets/alfa1/*.{jpeg,jpg,png,gif}"
);
const imageModulesSecond = import.meta.glob<{ default: ImageMetadata }>(
  "/src/assets/alfa2/*.{jpeg,jpg,png,gif}"
);
const imageModulesThird = import.meta.glob<{ default: ImageMetadata }>(
  "/src/assets/alfa3/*.{jpeg,jpg,png,gif}"
);

const sliderImagesFirst = await loadImages(imageModulesFirst);
const sliderImagesSecond = await loadImages(imageModulesSecond);
const sliderImagesThird = await loadImages(imageModulesThird);
---

<Layout {title} {years} logo={logoImg}>
  <ProjectContnetWrapper>
    <Text>
      Alfa-Bank is Russia's largest private bank, providing financial services
      to over 22 million customers through 672+ branches nationwide. As a
      universal bank, it offers comprehensive banking operations including
      retail, corporate banking, investment services, and digital solutions with
      approximately 25,000 employees.</Text
    >
    <Text class="mb-[1.562rem]"
      >Alfa Travel is the bank's integrated travel booking platform, providing
      comprehensive travel services including flights, hotels, train tickets,
      and vacation packages. The platform leverages the bank's ecosystem
      approach, allowing customers to utilize bonus points and rewards across
      all banking services while seamlessly booking and paying for travel
      through their existing banking relationship.</Text
    >
    <Heading level={2} size="xl" weight="semibold">My Role</Heading>
    <Text class="mb-[1.562rem]">
      Served as the sole designer within the travel services department,
      responsible for designing and enhancing the comprehensive travel booking
      platform. Working within Alfa Bank's established design system, I
      leveraged the bank's component library to create cohesive user experiences
      across flight bookings, hotel reservations, train tickets, and vacation
      packages while ensuring seamless integration with the broader banking
      ecosystem and rewards program.
    </Text>
    <Heading
      class="mt-[100px] mb-[10px] text-[28px]"
      level={2}
      weight="semibold">A Few Key Projects & Solutions</Heading
    >
    <Heading level={2} size="xl" weight="semibold"
      >Homepage Redesign & User Engagement</Heading
    >
    <Text class="mb-[25px]"
      >Redesigned the main travel platform interface using Alfa Bank's component
      library to create a cohesive search experience across all travel services.
      Implemented a flexible Bento-style banner system that dynamically
      accommodates varying quantities of promotional content, enabling both
      internal marketing and external partner advertising opportunities. Added
      "Popular Destinations," "Popular Hotels," and "Popular Tours" sections to
      increase user engagement and facilitate travel discovery through curated
      recommendations.</Text
    >
  </ProjectContnetWrapper>
  <div class="mt-[40px] mb-[100px]">
    <SwiperSlider sliderImages={sliderImagesFirst} initialWidth="267px" />
  </div>
  <ProjectContnetWrapper>
    <Heading level={2} size="xl" weight="semibold"
      >Automated Ticket Services</Heading
    >
    <Text class="mb-[1.562rem]">
      Developed self-service ticket refund and exchange system with automated
      price difference calculations, eliminating the need for customer support
      intervention. This solution reduced support inquiries for ticket-related
      issues by <b>74.1%</b>, significantly improving operational efficiency
      while providing users with instant ticket management capabilities.
    </Text>
  </ProjectContnetWrapper>
  <div class="mt-[40px] mb-[100px]">
    <SwiperSlider sliderImages={sliderImagesSecond} initialWidth="270px" />
  </div>
  <ProjectContnetWrapper>
    <Heading level={2} size="xl" weight="semibold"
      >Product Strategy Decision</Heading
    >
    <Text class="mb-[25px]">
      Given that clients were already using Excel-based workflows, we chose an
      MLP approach over basic MVP to reduce migration friction and deliver
      immediate value.
    </Text>
  </ProjectContnetWrapper>
  <ProjectContnetWrapper>
    <Heading level={2} size="xl" weight="semibold"
      >Enhanced Booking Experience</Heading
    >
    <Text class="mb-[60px]"
      >Created comprehensive booking workflows including airplane seat selection
      interfaces with visual seat maps, hotel booking system with interactive
      property search and maps, additional baggage services, SMS notification
      systems, digital ticket designs, and various auxiliary travel services to
      enhance the complete customer journey from search to post-travel
      experience.</Text
    >
  </ProjectContnetWrapper>
  <div class="mt-[40px] mb-[100px]">
    <SwiperSlider sliderImages={sliderImagesThird} initialWidth="270px" />
  </div>
</Layout>
